OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally fair days weather
OL,6,Fin prospect, mostly dry with with
OL,7,Frather cloudy skies but some
OL,8,Foccasional brighter or sunnier spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Winds northeasterly and
OL,10,Frelatively light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and settled evening
OL,13,Fwith light winds, Orkney seeing the
OL,14,Fbest of the late sunny periods. The
OL,15,Frest of the night will be dry for most
OL,16,Fwith clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
