OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA mostly dry and bright
OL,6,Fmorning with some hazy sunny spells.
OL,7,FTurning cloudier through the afternoon
OL,8,Ffor Orkney with the odd spot of rain,
OL,9,Fbut remaining mainly dry for Shetland.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable period with showers or
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain interspersed with
OL,14,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Winds
OL,15,Fgenerally southwesterly, fresh at
OL,16,Ftimes.
